                <div className="bg-slate-50 p-8 rounded-[3rem] border border-slate-200 text-center shadow-inner">
                    <p className="text-xs font-black text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-[0.3em] mb-2">ยอดชำระเงินรวมขณะนี้</p>
